itemLabel: Donald Nicholls, Baron Nicholls of Birkenhead
itemDescription: British lawyer and retired Law Lord (1933-2019)

wikipedia_page.main: Donald James Nicholls, Baron Nicholls of Birkenhead,  (25 January 1933 – 25 September 2019) was a British barrister who became a Law Lord (Lord of Appeal in Ordinary).
